These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Flower: lily, amaryllis, sunflower, iris
Game: snooker, monopoly, mah-jongg, go
1. Flower:sunflower is between Game:mah-jongg and Game:monopoly##2
2. Flower:iris is on the left or right of Game:mah-jongg##3
3. Game:mah-jongg is not to the left of Game:mah-jongg##8
4. Game:monopoly != Flower:sunflower##6
5. Flower:sunflower is somewhere to the right of Flower:lily##5
6. Flower:lily is on the right of Game:snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Flower   | iris  | lily | sunflower | amaryllis  |
| Game   | snooker | mah-jongg   | go  | monopoly |

