.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Hobby: card-games, baking, skydiving, rock-climbing
Color: blue, green, lilac, blood-red
1. Color:blood-red is not to the left of Color:blood-red##8
2. Hobby:card-games is somewhere to the right of Hobby:rock-climbing##5
3. Hobby:card-games == Color:green##1
4. Hobby:rock-climbing is between Hobby:card-games and Hobby:baking##2
5. Hobby:baking is somewhere between Hobby:skydiving and Color:blue##7
6. Color:lilac is somewhere to the left of Hobby:baking##5
7. Color:blue is not to the left of Color:blue##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby   | skydiving | baking          | rock-climbing | card-games     |
| Color    | lilac      | blood-red | blue | green |

