.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Birthday: august, november, december, march
Hobby: reading, woodworking, chess, photography
1. Hobby:reading is not to the left of Birthday:december##8
2. Hobby:woodworking is on the far left##1
3. Birthday:november is on the right of Birthday:august##1
4. Birthday:november is in an even position##4
5. Birthday:march is on the far left or far right##3
6. Birthday:august is somewhere to the left of Hobby:photography##5
7. Birthday:march == Hobby:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday           | august | november | december     | march |
| Hobby   | woodworking    | photography   | reading | chess    |

